code: @Test public void wrap() throws Exception {     XADataSource dataSource = mock(XADataSource.class).     BitronixXADataSourceWrapper wrapper = new BitronixXADataSourceWrapper().     DataSource wrapped = wrapper.wrapDataSource(dataSource).     assertThat(wrapped).isInstanceOf(PoolingDataSourceBean.class).     assertThat(((PoolingDataSourceBean) wrapped).getDataSource()).isSameAs(dataSource). }
